"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-features-paris-olympics-cross-country-course-pierre-le-goupil-versailles-course-designer-865208\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"French course-designer Pierre le Goupil expects theParis Olympicscross-country course to favour \\\"brave, positive riding and fast, reactive horses\\\" when the eventers tackle the track on Sunday (28 July).\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9644699956331839, \"rank\": 0.03594407722269858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"score\": 0.9935874826063947, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Goupil\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Goupil_&_Cie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicscross-country course\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"brave, positive riding\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 119}, {\"ngram\": \"the eventers\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 164}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The optimum time is 9min 2sec - over a minute longer than at theTokyo Olympics- over a distance of 5,149m.\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The optimum time\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 220}, {\"ngram\": \"9min 2sec\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"theTokyo\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics-\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"a distance\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"5,149m.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are 28 numbered fences, with a minimum of 45 jumping efforts.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"28 numbered fences\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"45 jumping efforts\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's more or less flat, and horses at this level should be fit enough, but you never know,\\\" says Pierre, who has used clever siting of the obstacles to slow riders down.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"clever siting\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"the obstacles\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"slow riders\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thewhole trackis stunningly crafted, with each fence having a theme or inspiration.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thewhole trackis\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"each fence\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"a theme\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"inspiration\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many are linked to the court of Louis XIV, who lived in the Palace of Versailles, but there are also nods to French literature, boat-building in the Grand Canal, and a spectacular stag's head with its antlers reaching up into the trees at 7m high.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\", \"score\": 0.9753206839054387, \"rank\": 0.02528061756747177, \"text\": \"Louis XIV\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louis_XIV\"}, {\"begin\": 748, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_literature\", \"score\": 0.9999999958513399, \"rank\": 4.148498116972965e-09, \"text\": \"French literature\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_literature\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_literature\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the Palace\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"nods\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"boat-building\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grand Canal\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular stag's head\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"its antlers\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"the trees\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is - in true French style - fantastically chic, with decorative touches such as realtoile de jouyFrench fabric cushions on a sofa fence and abundant wildflowers.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"decorative touches\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"realtoile de jouyFrench fabric cushions\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"a sofa fence\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"abundant wildflowers\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre is predicting optimum going and conditions, with a little rain forecast in the intervening days.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"optimum going\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"conditions\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"a little rain forecast\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the intervening days\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like much of Europe, deluges in spring meant that the building team had to postponed their installation until the end of May - 10 days behind schedule - as the ground was too wet.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"deluges\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"spring\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the building team\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"their installation\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"schedule\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Pierre had worked hard on ensuring the ground would hold up well.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the parts of the course that needed reseeding, you can hear a crunchy sound as you walk, almost sounding like gravel.\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the parts\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"reseeding\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"a crunchy sound\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"gravel\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is thanks to a volcanic soil he has laid down, which breaks up as it is trampled, drains well and allows for excellent grass growth.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"a volcanic soil\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"excellent grass growth\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I discovered it by accident when I was working on a trotting track in Lignieres and used some of the spare volcanic soil they had,\\\" he explains.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accident\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"a trotting track\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"Lignieres\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"the spare volcanic soil\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I came back a year later, that ground was better than anywhere else.\\\"\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that ground\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The forecast for cross-country day is around 26\\u00baC, with the last rider scheduled to start around 2.30pm.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The forecast\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"cross-country day\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the last rider\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre expects horses to cope well with a typical French summer's day.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9644699956331839, \"rank\": 0.03594407722269858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"More than half the course is in the shade of the trees, and the Grand Canal brings down the heat as well,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than half the course\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"the shade\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"the trees\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grand Canal\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Conditions should be perfect.\\\"\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conditions\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The course has a flowing feel to it, with no sharp turn-backs, and long galloping stretches.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The course\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"a flowing feel\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"no sharp turn-backs\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"long galloping stretches\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre says: \\\"When I first heard about the cross country being at Versailles, I thought, 'It's going to be flat.\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"the cross country\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Straight lines, sharp turns, nothing to play with', and it's totally different.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Straight lines\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"sharp turns\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot of things to play with.\\\"\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, there are several spots where he has put a so-called let-up fence on a bending line, or added some decoration in between fences, to slow riders down without making the horses uncomfortable.\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several spots\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"a so-called let-up fence\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"a bending line\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"some decoration\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"fences\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Equally, the long routes at fences are circuitous so in many cases will add plenty of time, but will not put pressure on tiring horses by needing them to twist and double back on themselves.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the long routes\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"fences\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"many cases\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"tiring horses\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre wasappointed as Paris Olympics cross-country course-designer in 2022and has visited the Versailles venue some 60 times over the past two years, and spent \\\"six or seven weeks\\\" of the past two months on site.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2965, \"end\": 2979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"2022and\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"the Versailles\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two years\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"six or seven weeks\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two months\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Versailles is a virgin eventing site, although it has hosted a showjumping competition in the past.\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Versailles\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"a virgin eventing site\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"a showjumping competition\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of the water fences have been specially created, while the first water is a renovation of an existing fountain site in a former exotic menagerie.\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water fences\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"the first water\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"a renovation\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"an existing fountain site\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"a former exotic menagerie\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the event is over, all the groundworks will be restored to their original state.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"all the groundworks\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"their original state\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pierre paid particular tribute to the course-builder Christian Aschard, who will retire after this event, and all the craftsmen and artists who have contributed to this spectacular track.\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3548, \"end\": 3557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9453699903196874, \"rank\": 0.03832259325442156, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3501}, {\"ngram\": \"particular tribute\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"all the craftsmen\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"this spectacular track\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the lucky one who gets to design the track, but the designers are only as good as their builders and it's the builders who do not enough credit,\\\" says Pierre.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lucky one\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3703}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"the designers\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"their builders\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"the builders\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"not enough credit\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"Pierre\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have relied on a high level of skill.\\\"\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high level\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"skill\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's exactly what the riders will need, both in themselves and their horses, to tackle the challenge he has set.\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 4010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3915}, {\"ngram\": \"the riders\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3926}, {\"ngram\": \"their horses\", \"from\": 3961, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 3998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our expert team of reporters and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4143, \"end\": 4156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4035}, {\"ngram\": \"all the news\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4053}, {\"ngram\": \"the run-up\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4067}, {\"ngram\": \"the major shows\", \"from\": 4086, \"to\": 4101}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4112}, {\"ngram\": \"todayfor\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4188}, {\"ngram\": \"these major events\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4237}, {\"ngram\": \"online reports\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4258}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4272}, {\"ngram\": \"our expert team\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4307}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 4311, \"to\": 4320}, {\"ngram\": \"depth\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4333}, {\"ngram\": \"our special commemorative magazines\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have a subscription already?Set up your unlimited website access now\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a subscription already?Set\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4414}, {\"ngram\": \"your unlimited website access\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4447}]}]}"